txt.en: 'Hail, [placeholder]! You assisted in defeating Núrzum, but enemies still roam our lands and lurk in the shadows.\n\n'Gîmtog terrorizes the eastern edge of the Whitshaws. Go there, and show him that Wildermore will endure!'
You have defeated Gîmtog, earning the gratitude of the people of Wildermore.
<rgb=#FF0000>Completing Wildermore's Recovery will cancel this quest.</rgb>
Núrzum has been defeated, but enemies persist throughout much of Wildermore. Gîmtog terrorizes the eastern edge of the Whitshaws.
Gîmtog can be found patrolling the eastern edge of the Whitshaws with a pack of vicious wolves.
You have defeated Gîmtog, earning the gratitude of the people of Wildermore.
